dcterms:description: PoseIt is a multi-modal dataset that contains visual and tactile data collected from a full cycle of grasping an object, repositioning the arm to one of the sampled poses, and shaking the object to check its stability. It consists of 1840 grasp datapoints collected from 26 distinct objects, with 16 different holding poses for each object.
dcterms:title: PoseIt
